{"tid":1550582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[twitter]呢位一直幫我地好多既外國人翻譯左篇野幫我地宣傳","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T02:06:57.000Z","uid":35478,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"69649714d8a666d6e7f4b42b9c4fa1b5de28f41a","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該有twitter既人介唔介意幫佢retweet下, <br />\n甚至follow埋佢?<br />\n佢一直都好支持我地呢場運動<br />\n甚至幫我地海外宣傳左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1170309964457369601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1170309964457369601&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=10611f8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1170309964457369601&h=3c86ada1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1170309964457369601</a><br />\n佢話呢篇野好令人感動<br />\n相信呢篇文章可以令到好多唔太了解外國人支持我地 <br />\n知道我地年輕一輩到底係呢場運動做左D咩 係受左咩逼害<br />\n外國既和理非受眾應該好受落呢一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩所有人見到幫手retweet下<br />\n麻煩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e19e25f30a19398d10109ecf97f5920a2bca9f5","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fc2d67c4f9f16d38267fb7dec7b0eddabd99b0","tid":1550582,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b45ef5dedcc183b130acc20c9640b1495351b04b","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecb14caf34c49814dcef62caf56990d7414b88b","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5002e731723c60f51d807064f1711a32e8f08380","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb3ae4a36643ab000a78c59a3d6e2b51a0efe8e","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e7d17eadffeeabe0e3aa6d5ea270e7a3859684","tid":1550582,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"全港連儂牆要人，文宣要人！<br />\n<br />\n8/9 美領事館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衛城長久戰，全民都抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=cd5f0037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"7a3ca50810d935b25f65392e7c44bacded2f168b","tid":1550582,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1f628b97a67b455d353c7503edbeccf9b8fdaa","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a3ca50810d935b25f65392e7c44bacded2f168b","tid":1550582,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"d9c423eb8da82a11d8e9f9d2352d7cfddb5cdbf1","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa52cf07a18b9fbf7108035ff2fa865f1a51ed5b","tid":1550582,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cl